parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission pulse generator can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to sudden downshifting, jerking, and loss of control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The transmission downshifts violently
the transmission shifts back into higher gear with a violent jerk
the vehicle experiences temporary loss of control
the vehicle jerks hard when accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature mechanical failure of the transmission can cause the transmission to malfunction or fail, leading to sudden loss of power, stalling, or difficulty shifting gears, which can increase the risk of accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission drops out of gear
the transmission fails to engage properly
the vehicle experiences sudden loss of power
the vehicle stalls.
